Description: Siemens S7 communication library (Python 3)
 This is a Python wrapper for Snap7, an open-source, 32/64 bit,
 multi-platform Ethernet communication suite for interfacing natively
 with Siemens S7 PLCs.
 .
 This package installs the library for Python 3.

